Valdes previously hinted at the idea of erasing himself from the internet in a 2015 interview with Catalan media outlet RAC1, saying: &ldquo;When the light goes out someday, then it will go out and I&rsquo;ll be with my children, teaching them about life.&rdquo;<br />
<br />
&ldquo;But I hope that when the light does go out, it will be hard to find me.&rdquo;
